ist-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"><strong style="list-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;"></strong></span>验房是业主在收房前，为避免因房产存在的瑕疵或缺陷没有得到及时发现和解决，入住后引发纠纷或不必要的麻烦，而在收房前对房屋进行查验的行为 墙面空鼓,墙体渗水,门窗破损,管道损坏，护栏装置,电气设备安装不符规范······入住之后可能引发不便，甚至存在安全隐患. (开发商在新房)交付前，要通知购房人先对房屋进行查验，查验后要填写查验表和维修表，然后才依据合同的约定办理交付手续.</span><br style="list-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);"/><span style="list-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong style="list-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">为什么要验房?</strong></span><span style="list-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); line-height: 32px;"><span style="list-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;"><strong style="list-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;"></strong></span>&nbsp;</span><span style="list-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">房屋作为一种特殊的商品，势必存在各种质量问题.但由于房屋的构造，包含了诸多的专业知识，因此并不是每一位购房者都能够清楚地掌握.而这些问题，如果被忽视，就有可能给购房者造成损失或在日后的使用中带来不必要的麻烦.</span><span style="list-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);">&nbsp;</span><span style="list-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">我们的宗旨就是通过我们的专业知识，通过我们全力尽心的验房服务，让购房者清楚明白的知道自己所购置物业存在的问题，让购房者通过我们的服务，和我们一样专业，从而更好的维权.</span><br style="list-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);"/><span style="list-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong style="list-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;">什么是量房?</strong></span><span style="list-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); line-height: 28px;"><span style="list-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; line-height: 32px;"><strong style="list-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent;"></strong></span>&nbsp;<span style="list-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">量房是装修的开始，通常由设计师参与，对业主的房型进行具体的测量,记录.</span></span><br style="list-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);"/><span style="list-style: none; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); word-wrap: break-word; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; line-hei